.rule_6_6_9_ensure_local_passwords_require_multiple_character_sets

Reference: Agency (NSA) Payment Card Industry Data Security Standard (PCI DSS), Version 1.2,
Requirement 8.5.

Remediation: Configure a password character set changes using the following command under the [edit
system] hierarchy:
[edit system]
user@host#set login password change-type character-set






